<br>
Here's the story:<br>
<br>
I traded an Arbitors Combine Greatsword, and a pair of GEBs for a regen BP, which in my opinion is about a fair trade. After realising i would prefer good weapons to the BP, i go to EC tunnel and start auctioning &quot;WTT Regen BP and FBSS for a pair of Lammys&quot; (Again in my opinion a fair trade&quot;<br>
<br>
So then Pidnus starts his spam<br>
<br>
&quot; Sell the BP for 15, not 20, u will never get 20&quot;<br>
&quot;I will give u a Lam for the BP&quot;<br>
&quot;Give me the BP, FBSS and 5k for the pair of lams&quot;<br>
&quot;yadda yadda yadda.....&quot;<br>
<br>
So on this goes for 30mins or so. I keep my trade auction going for a while. Then a friend of mine needs a Corpse summon in Sol B, so i log my necro on, and start heading that way from EC tunnel. Before i zone into Nek forest, I do one last auction of &quot;WTT Regen BP for Lam and 4k&quot;. Two minutes go by, and no response, so i zone into Nek Forest.<br>
<br>
Half way through my run to Lavastorm, i get a tell from a guy called Soultyrant saying &quot;I will give u Lam and 5k for the BP&quot;.<br>
OK, so i am in a bit of a dilema now, cus i got someone needing a corpse summon, but really wanna make the trade, so I log Naklak back on quickly, and meet Soultyrant in EC tunnel. He gives me the Lam, and tells me the 5k is on his main character &quot;Nubby&quot; (hang my head in shame). I am in such a rush i stick the BP in the window and ask him to hurry please. He makes the trade, says BRB, and then goes invis and dashes off.<br>
Well after waiting 5 mins, and doing constant /who all Soultyrant, and /who all nubby I realise I have been had.<br>
<br>
Ok, so now i am IMMENSLY pissed off about losing 5k, but then I get a tell from Pidnus saying, &quot;Wow, i cant believe i got a regen BP!!&quot;. I say &quot;WTF? Was it u who just scammed me?&quot; to which he replies &quot;No, I got the BP from Bulok&quot;.<br>
About a minute later Bulok tells me &quot;Still got the BP?, I will buy it from you&quot;<br>
<br>
/em cries<br>
<br>
Ok, so that night I was pissed off for losing 5k, but now having read this board, realising Pid-shit is Bulok, and has a necro twink (BTW - Soultyrant was a necro), I feel as though i have been a victim of his scam.<br>
<br>
I have no idea what to do about it, cus it happened about a week ago, and GMs will do nothing no doubt, and it's not as if i can harass Pidnus ingame, cus (a) He will prolly petition and it will be ME who gets in trouble, and (b) Text on a screen isnt sufficient, i actually want to phsyically hurt the guy.<br>
<br>
Sorry this is long winded, but that's how it happened, and i would suggest u avoid Pidnus / Bulok / Soultyrant at all costs.<br>
